    <DIV class="headRightCurveblk"></DIV>
    <DIV class="contentbox">
        <p>
            Verizon Wireless views its music services broadly, encompassing the full
            gamut of multimedia products and services the company currently offers,
            as well as potential future services. These services include:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>V CAST Music (music on demand)</li>
            <li>V CAST Music Videos</li>
            <li>Wallpaper art (including album covers, images of music-makers)</li>
            <li>Concert broadcasts</li>
            <li>Ringtones</li>
            <li>Ringback tones (heard by a caller while the Verizon Wireless customer's phone is 'ringing')</li>
            <li>TXT messaging (at concert venues, to large-screens)</li>
            <li>… and more!</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            V CAST Music runs on Verizon Wireless' broadband network, available to about 150
            million people from coast to coast. V CAST Music is available through Verizon
            Wireless' 2,000 Communications Stores and Circuit City locations and online at
